An influencer is a person who has the ability to
influence the opinions, thoughts, or behaviors of
others through their presence on social media or
other platforms. Influencers often have a large
following on platforms such as Instagram,
YouTube, or TikTok, and they use their platforms
to share content with their followers, often
related to a particular topic or area of
expertise. They may also collaborate with brands
or companies to promote products or services to
their followers. Influencers are often seen as
